#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md:1
msgid "优化算法的区别与使用情境"
msgstr "Optimization Algorithms: Differences and Use Cases"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md:3
msgid "为何需要了解不同算法"
msgstr "Why Learn About Different Algorithms"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md:5
msgid ""
"参数空间与计算成本差异大：网格搜索在小空间上可靠但组合爆炸；启发式或贝叶斯在有限评估次数下权衡精度与速度；不同算法对连续/离散/混合参数的支持也不同。"
msgstr ""
"Parameterräume und Rechenkosten variieren stark: Die Rastersuche ist in "
"kleinen Räumen zuverlässig, explodiert jedoch kombinatorisch; Bei "
"Heuristiken oder Bayes'schen Methoden geht es bei einem begrenzten "
"Evaluierungsbudget um Genauigkeit gegen Geschwindigkeit. Algorithmen "
"unterscheiden sich auch in der Unterstützung kontinuierlicher, diskreter "
"oder gemischter Parameter."

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md:7
msgid "各优化算法对比（罗列并说明区别）"
msgstr "Vergleich von Optimierungsalgorithmen (mit Unterschieden aufgeführt)"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "算法"
msgstr "Algorithm"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "原理简述"
msgstr "Brief Principle"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "优点与局限"
msgstr "Pros and Limitations"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "适用参数规模"
msgstr "Typical Parameter Scale"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "连续/离散/混合"
msgstr "Continuous / Discrete / Mixed"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "典型计算成本"
msgstr "Typical Compute Cost"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "grid"
msgstr "grid"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "在网格点上穷举或遍历"
msgstr "Exhaustive search or traversal on grid points"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "实现简单、结果可复现；维数高时不可行"
msgstr "Simple and reproducible; impractical in high dimensions"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "小（2～3 维）"
msgstr "Small (2–3 dimensions)"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "离散为主"
msgstr "Mostly discrete"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "随点数线性增长"
msgstr "Grows linearly with grid size"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "montecarlo"
msgstr "montecarlo"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "随机采样参数组合"
msgstr "Random sampling of parameter combinations"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "实现简单、易并行；需较多样本才稳定"
msgstr ""
"Einfach und leicht zu parallelisieren; benötigt viele Proben für die "
"Stabilität"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "中、大"
msgstr "Medium to large"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "均可"
msgstr "All supported"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "由 sample_count 决定"
msgstr "Determined by ``sample_count``"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "GA"
msgstr "GA"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "遗传、交叉、变异"
msgstr "Selection, crossover, mutation"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "适合非凸、多峰；调参敏感"
msgstr ""
"Geeignet für nicht-konvexe, multimodale Probleme; hyperparameterempfindlich"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "由代数与种群规模决定"
msgstr "Determined by generations and population size"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "SA"
msgstr "SA"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "模拟退火、概率接受劣解"
msgstr "Simuliertes Glühen; akzeptiert wahrscheinlich schlechtere Lösungen"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "可跳出局部最优；收敛较慢"
msgstr "Can escape local optima; slower convergence"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "中"
msgstr "Medium"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "由迭代次数决定"
msgstr "Determined by iteration count"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "PSO"
msgstr "PSO"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "粒子群位置与速度更新"
msgstr "Particle swarm position and velocity updates"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "连续空间表现好；离散需编码"
msgstr "Strong in continuous spaces; discrete params need encoding"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "连续为主"
msgstr "Mostly continuous"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "由粒子数与迭代决定"
msgstr "Determined by particle count and iterations"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "bayesian"
msgstr "bayesian"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "代理模型+采集函数"
msgstr "Surrogate model + acquisition function"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "样本少时效率高；高维成本高"
msgstr "Efficient with few samples; costly in high dimensions"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "小、中"
msgstr "Small to medium"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md
msgid "由迭代与模型拟合决定"
msgstr "Determined by iterations and model fitting"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md:18
msgid "使用情境与选择建议"
msgstr "Use Cases and Selection Advice"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md:20
msgid "**参数少、离散**：优先 grid 或小规模 montecarlo。"
msgstr ""
"**Few discrete parameters**: Prefer ``grid`` or small-scale ``montecarlo``."

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md:21
msgid "**参数多、需少步数**：考虑 bayesian 或 GA/PSO。"
msgstr ""
"**Many parameters, few evaluation steps**: Consider ``bayesian`` or "
"``GA``/``PSO``."

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md:22
msgid "**连续空间、多峰**：PSO、GA 或 SA。"
msgstr "**Continuous, multi-modal space**: ``PSO``, ``GA``, or ``SA``."

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md:23
msgid ""
"**opti_sample_count、参数个数**：样本或迭代不足时，启发式可能早停；可适当增大 opti_sample_count 或降低参数维度。"
msgstr ""
"**``opti_sample_count`` und Parameteranzahl**: Bei zu wenigen Stichproben "
"oder Iterationen kann die Heuristik vorzeitig beendet werden; Erhöhen Sie "
"„opti_sample_count“ oder reduzieren Sie die Parameterdimensionalität nach "
"Bedarf."

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md:25
msgid "简要对比表"
msgstr "Quick Comparison Table"

#: ../../source/optimization/3. optimization_algorithms.md:27
msgid ""
"见上表；实施时以当前 qteasy 支持的 opti_method 及文档为准，注意各算法的典型参数（如 GA "
"的种群大小、变异率等）在配置中的名称与默认值。"
msgstr ""
"Siehe die Tabelle oben. Befolgen Sie in der Praxis die „opti_method“-Werte, "
"die von der aktuellen qteasy-Version und ihren Dokumenten unterstützt "
"werden; Beachten Sie die typischen Einstellungen jedes Algorithmus (z. B. "
"GA-Populationsgröße und Mutationsrate) sowie deren Konfigurationsnamen und "
"Standardeinstellungen."
